OL,3,CMan smuggled 29,000 skull-shaped
OL,4,Cecstasy tablets in Snapchat deal
OL,6,FA man who tried to import tens of
OL,7,Fthousands of ecstasy tablets to South
OL,8,FTyneside via the postal system in a
OL,9,Fdeal arranged over Snapchat has been
OL,10,Fjailed.
OL,12,FThe National Crime Agency (NCA) was
OL,13,Fnotified by Border Force officers at
OL,14,FBirmingham Airport that a parcel had
OL,15,Fbeen intercepted and found to contain
OL,16,F29,000 green skull-shaped tablets.
OL,18,FIt had been sent from the Netherlands
OL,19,Fand was addressed to Marshall
OL,20,FScurfield, 22, who at the time lived
OL,21,Fin Coniston Avenue, in Hebburn.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
