OL,3,CMan smuggled 29,000 skull-shaped
OL,4,Cecstasy tablets in Snapchat deal
OL,6,FThe tablets later tested positive for
OL,7,FMDMA and had an estimated street value
OL,8,Fof #140,000.
OL,10,FAs part of the investigation the
OL,11,Ftablets were removed and a dummy
OL,12,Fpackage was sent to Scurfield, who had
OL,13,Fbeen receiving parcel tracking updates
OL,14,Fvia Snapchat.
OL,16,FHe was arrested by NCA officers on 25
OL,17,FFebruary 2022 after being observed
OL,18,Faccepting the package.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
