OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F421A1733249386
OL,3,CMan smuggled 29,000 skull-shaped
OL,4,Cecstasy tablets in Snapchat deal
OL,6,FWhen questioned, Scurfield admitted
OL,7,Fthat he had agreed to accept the
OL,8,Fparcel to settle a drugs debt, and
OL,9,Fthat arrangements for its delivery had
OL,10,Fbeen made using Snapchat.
OL,12,FHe was charged with importing class A
OL,13,Fdrugs and admitted the offence at
OL,14,FNewcastle Crown Court on 2 July this
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FScurfield, who now lives in Airdrie,
OL,18,FNorth Lanarkshire, was sentenced to
OL,19,Ffour years imprisonment at the same
OL,20,Fcourt on Tuesday (3 December).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
