OL,3,CMan smuggled 29,000 skull-shaped
OL,4,Cecstasy tablets in Snapchat deal
OL,6,FNCA branch commander Martin Clarke
OL,7,Fsaid: "Marshall Scurfield attempted to
OL,8,Fimport dangerous class A drugs into
OL,9,Fthe UK and thought that by using the
OL,10,Fpostal system he would escape
OL,11,Fattention from law enforcement.
OL,13,F"Working with our colleagues at Border
OL,14,FForce, we were able to prevent a
OL,15,Fsizeable quantity of ecstasy from
OL,16,Fmaking it to our streets, where it
OL,17,Fwould have created exploitation and
OL,18,Fviolence.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
